title: Firefly - The Complete Score
description:
This is every bit of music from the TV Series &quot;Firefly.&quot;

Thanks to Sneaker98 at www.fireflyfans.net for creating these files.

They are taken from the DVD's, and as such, the sound effects, dialogue, etc. are still present.  Deal with it.

I merely gained and tagged them.  Its not perfect, but in the absence of an Original Soundtrack, it will do!  Enjoy.
